{"tid":598273,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"［火影］宇智波富岳vs宇智波鼬","createTime":"2018-03-19T11:12:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-19T11:40:24.000Z","uid":64694,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1c3515bf17fda5cdfe38c1dfbe85928538873586","tid":598273,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T11:12:18.000Z","msg":"宇智波富岳：<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/19/190611_5b9f998c0d0cbdd398a44b64c63038be.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F19%2F190611_5b9f998c0d0cbdd398a44b64c63038be.png&h=887bce07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n宇智波鼬：<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/19/190612_012690e849507c7a74efa87533232cea.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F19%2F190612_012690e849507c7a74efa87533232cea.png&h=52ef519d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鼬殺雙親：<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/19/190613_a084c0b4488d64f4539d8e06305e9947.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F19%2F190613_a084c0b4488d64f4539d8e06305e9947.png&h=30a1b216&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n鼬未殺雙親之前，富岳同鼬一樣有萬花筒寫輪眼，但富岳俾鼬殺之前無諗住反抗，係因為唔想鼬難做，定抑或係覺得自己實力已經俾唔上鼬？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f4d2680d5f898d8fbb48a51731da8d841fa1284","tid":598273,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T11:13:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>宇智波富岳：<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/19/190611_5b9f998c0d0cbdd398a44b64c63038be.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F19%2F190611_5b9f998c0d0cbdd398a44b64c63038be.png&h=887bce07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n宇智波鼬：<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/19/190612_012690e849507c7a74efa87533232cea.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F19%2F190612_012690e849507c7a74efa87533232cea.png&h=52ef519d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鼬殺雙親：<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/19/190613_a084c0b4488d64f4539d8e06305e9947.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F19%2F190613_a084c0b4488d64f4539d8e06305e9947.png&h=30a1b216&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n鼬未殺雙親之前，富岳同鼬一樣有萬花筒寫輪眼，但富岳俾鼬殺之前無諗住反抗，係因為唔想鼬難做，定抑或係覺得自己實力已經<span style=\"color: red;\">比唔</span>上鼬？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"054dec835234314d6e6e024c952fc3b27c466ef5","tid":598273,"uid":91502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T11:15:55.000Z","msg":"夠唔夠做唔肯定 但照睇都幾肯定佢唔係因為咁而坐定定比佢殺"},{"pid":"0a456d27006c312c5e52ad1310a2cf80fdc9984a","tid":598273,"uid":123175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T11:23:24.000Z","msg":"富嶽應該係計啱條數先公子獻頭<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n鼬本身戰力就好高<br />\n富嶽個政變計劃應該都考慮到要大仔參與先可能成事<br />\n<br />\n但係鼬率先叛變<br />\n此消彼長<br />\n若此時執行家法，處決鼬等於自斷半臂<br />\n之後根本無力抗衡木葉<br />\n最後可能完全冚家剷<br />\n<br />\n反而留兩個仔一命<br />\n只要血脈未斷，內輪一族仲有中興嘅機會"},{"pid":"683270f369fa1d03f67b6a82a17e08d0205b568b","tid":598273,"uid":18350,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T11:27:21.000Z","msg":"漫畫邊度有講佢老豆有萬華鏡"},{"pid":"1e3fda140e61bd1c9bdc4d22684c687abf59d620","tid":598273,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"683270f369fa1d03f67b6a82a17e08d0205b568b","tid":598273,"uid":18350,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T11:27:21.000Z","msg":"漫畫邊度有講佢老豆有萬華鏡"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T11:31:17.000Z","msg":"鼬真傳，好似係"},{"pid":"178c172ffe2edd2778941289eaa3782977552b14","tid":598273,"uid":48887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T11:40:24.000Z","msg":"仔大仔世界啦"}]}